nt developments in artificial intelligence in healthcare'}, {'title': 'Result 1 for challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare', 'url': 'https://example.com/challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare/1', 'snippet': 'This is a snippet for the first result about challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare'}, {'title': 'Result 2 for challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare', 'url': 'https://example.com/challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare/2', 'snippet': 'This is another result related to challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare showing important information'}, {'title': 'Result 3 for challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare', 'url': 'https://example.com/challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare/3', 'snippet': 'Third result providing additional context about challenges and opportunities in artificial intelligence in healthcare'}], 'synthesized_knowledge': \"Based on research about 'artificial intelligence in healthcare', key findings include: This is a snippet for the first result about overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare; This is another result related to overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare showing important information; Third result providing additional context about overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare\", 'sources': ['https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/1', 'https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/2', 'https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/3', 'https://example.com/recent developments in artificial intelligence in healthcare/1', 'https://example.com/recent developments in artificial intelligence in healthcare/2'], 'research_steps': ['Research plan for \\'artificial intelligence in healthcare\\':\\n1. Search for overview\\n2. Find recent developments\\n3. Identify challenges and opportunities', 'Executed 3 searches and collected 9 results', 'Synthesized information from 9 sources', 'Generated final report on artificial intelligence in healthcare'], 'final_report': \"Research Report on 'artificial intelligence in healthcare':\\nBased on research about 'artificial intelligence in healthcare', key findings include: This is a snippet for the first result about overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare; This is another result related to overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare showing important information; Third result providing additional context about overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare\\n\\nSources consulted: ['https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/1', 'https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/2', 'https://example.com/overview of artificial intelligence in healthcare/3', 'https://example.com/recent developments in artificial intelligence in healthcare/1', 'https://example.com/recent developments in artificial intelligence in healthcare/2']\"}\n"
     ]
